    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-1a' );" name="007-1a" class="pb">[007-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:210'>　經禮補逸卷七　　　　　元　汪克寛　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='210:216'>　　軍禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='216:224'>　　　振旅禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='224:247'>書大禹謨禹班師振旅周禮大司馬中春敎振旅司馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='247:270'>以旗致民平列陳如戰之陳辨鼓鐸鐲鐃之用王執路</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='270:293'>鼓諸侯執賁鼓軍將執晉鼓師帥執提旅帥執鼙卒長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='293:316'>執鐃兩司馬執鐸公司馬執鐲以敎坐作進退疾徐疏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='316:342'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-1b' );" name="007-1b" class="pb">[007-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='342:373'>數之節大宰作大事則戒于百官賛王命<span class='krp-note'>謂助王為敎/令案春秋傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='373:403'><span class='krp-note'>國之大事/在祀與戎</span>小宰以法掌祭祀朝覲㑹同賔客之戒具軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='403:426'>旅田役喪荒亦如之令百官府共其財用治其施舍聽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='426:449'>其治訟大司馬若大師則掌其戒令涖太卜帥執事涖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='449:472'>釁主及軍器司戈盾軍旅授貳車戈盾建乗車之戈盾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='472:495'>授旅賁及虎士戈盾司弓矢凡師役頒弓弩授兵甲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='495:518'>儀司常凡軍事建旌旗大司徒大軍役以旗致萬民而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='518:541'>治其徒庶之政令大僕凡軍旅賛王鼓鼔人以鼖鼓鼓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='541:567'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-2a' );" name="007-2a" class="pb">[007-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='567:590'>軍事凡軍旅夜鼓鼜軍動則鼓其衆巾車掌王之五路</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='590:613'>革路龍勒條纓五就建太白以即戎車僕掌戎路之萃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='613:636'>廣車之萃闕車之萃苹車之萃輕車之萃凡師共革車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='636:659'>各以其萃典路凡軍旅以路從銜枚氏軍旅令銜枚禁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='659:682'>嘂呼歎鳴於國中者大師執同律以聽軍聲而詔吉凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='682:705'>幕人軍旅共其帷幕幄帟綬掌次師田則張幕設重帟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='705:728'>重案廩人凡師役之事則治其糧與其食封人軍旅則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='728:751'>飾其牛牲外饔師役則掌共其獻賜脯肉之事委人軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='751:777'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-2b' );" name="007-2b" class="pb">[007-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='777:800'>旅共其委積薪蒭遺人凡師役掌其道路之委積小子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='800:823'>凡師田斬牲以左右徇陳牛人軍事共其犒牛凡軍旅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='823:846'>行役共其兵車之牛小行人若國師役則令槁禬之縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='846:869'>師若將有軍旅田役之戒則受法于司馬以作其衆庶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='869:892'>及馬牛車輦會其車人之卒伍使皆備旗鼓兵器以帥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='892:915'>而至大司寇凡大軍旅涖戮于社士師大師帥其屬而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='915:938'>禁逆軍旅者與犯師禁者而戮之鄉士大軍旅則各掌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='938:952'>其鄉之禁令帥其屬夾道而蹕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='952:978'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-3a' );" name="007-3a" class="pb">[007-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='978:986'>　　　茇舍禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='986:1009'>大司馬中夏敎茇舍如振旅之陳羣吏撰車徒讀書契</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1009:1032'>辨號名之用帥以門名縣鄙各以其名家以號名鄉以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1032:1055'>州名野以邑名百官各象其事以辨軍之夜事其他皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1055:1060'>如振旅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1060:1067'>　　治兵禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1067:1090'>大司馬中秋敎治兵如振旅之陳辨旗物之用王載大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1090:1113'>常諸侯載旂軍吏載旗師都載旜鄉遂載物郊野載旐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1113:1139'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-3b' );" name="007-3b" class="pb">[007-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1139:1159'>百官載旟各書其事與其號焉其他皆如振旅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1159:1167'>　　　大閲禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1167:1190'>大司馬中冬敎大閲前期羣吏戒衆庶修戰法虞人萊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1190:1213'>所田之野為表百步則一為三表又五十步為一表田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1213:1236'>之日司馬建旗于後表之中羣吏以旗物鼔鐸鐲鐃各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1236:1259'>帥其民而致質明弊旗追後至者乃陳車徒如戰之陳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1259:1282'>皆坐羣吏聽誓于陳前斬牲以左右徇陳曰不用命者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1282:1305'>斬之中軍以鼙令鼓鼓人皆三鼓司馬振鐸羣吏作旗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1305:1331'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-4a' );" name="007-4a" class="pb">[007-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1331:1354'>車徒皆作鼓行鳴鐲車徒皆行及表乃止三鼓摝鐸羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1354:1377'>吏弊旗車徒皆坐又三鼓振鐸作旗車徒皆作鼓進鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1377:1400'>鐲車驟徒趨及表乃止坐作如初乃鼔車馳徒走及表</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1400:1423'>乃止鼓戒三闋車三發徒三刺乃鼓退鳴鐃且郤及表</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1423:1446'>乃止坐作如初司常掌九旗之物名各有屬以待國事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1446:1469'>日月為常交龍為旂通帛為旜雜帛為物熊虎為旗鳥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1469:1492'>隼為旟龜蛇為旐全羽為旞析羽為旌及國之大閱賛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1492:1515'>司馬頒旗物王建大常諸侯建旂孤卿建旜大夫士建</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1515:1541'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-4b' );" name="007-4b" class="pb">[007-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1541:1564'>物師都建旗州里建旟縣鄙建旐道車建旞斿車載旌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1564:1583'>皆畫其象焉春秋桓公六年八月壬午大閲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1583:1606'>　愚案周禮先王寓軍政於四時之田不廢武備中春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1606:1629'>　敎振旅以敎坐作進退疾徐疏數之節中夏敎茇舍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1629:1652'>　以辨號名之用中秋敎治兵以辨旗物之用其他皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1652:1675'>　如振旅然其法畧於三時而致備於中冬者為農隙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1675:1698'>　也故於是時簡車徒精器物屬旗鼓以敎衆庶修戰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1698:1721'>　法斬牲徇陳而訓誓之使耳目之衆莫不一心驟趨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1721:1747'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-5a' );" name="007-5a" class="pb">[007-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1747:1770'>　之節無有異習誅一庸慢甄一用命改易視聽以作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1770:1793'>　其勇敢之氣而民趨勞如趨逸者蓋以其令之素敎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1793:1816'>　之善也今桓公乃大閲於煩暑之月不惟妨民失政</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1816:1839'>　之非而妄為僭禮之舉是豈事上臨下之道先王敎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1839:1857'>　民之意哉故春秋特書之以垂戒焉耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1857:1865'>　　　蒐田禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1865:1888'>大司馬中春敎振旅遂以蒐田有司表貉誓民鼓遂圍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1888:1911'>禁火弊獻禽以祭社大司徒大田役以旗致萬民而治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1911:1937'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-5b' );" name="007-5b" class="pb">[007-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1937:1960'>其徒庶之政令縣正若將用野民師田行役移執事則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1960:1983'>帥而至治其政令既役則稽功㑹事而誅賞鄉師凡四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1983:2006'>時之田前期出田法于州里簡其鼓鐸旗物兵器修其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2006:2029'>卒伍及期以司徒之大旗致衆庶而陳之以旗物辨鄉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2029:2052'>邑而治其政令刑禁巡其前後之屯而戮其犯命者斷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2052:2075'>其争禽之訟稍人若有師田行役之事則以縣師之法</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2075:2098'>作其同徒輂輦帥而至治其政令以聽於司馬小宗伯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2098:2121'>若大田則帥有司而饁獸于郊遂頒禽肆師凡四時之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2121:2147'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-6a' );" name="007-6a" class="pb">[007-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2147:2170'>大甸獵祭表貉則為位遂師軍旅田獵平野民掌其禁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2170:2193'>令比敘其事而賞罰遂人師田作野民帥而至掌其政</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2193:2216'>治禁令甸祝掌四時之田表貉之祝號禂牲掌其祝號</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2216:2239'>小宰以法掌朝覲㑹同賔客之戒具軍旅田役亦如之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2239:2262'>令百官府共其財用治其施舍聽其治訟小子凡師田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2262:2285'>斬牲以左右徇陳巾車掌王之五路木路前樊鵠纓建</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2285:2308'>大麾以田田僕掌馭田路以田以鄙掌佐車之政設驅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2308:2331'>逆之車令獲者植旌及獻比禽凡田王提馬而走諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2331:2357'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-6b' );" name="007-6b" class="pb">[007-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2357:2380'>晉大夫馳校人田獵則帥驅逆之車幕人田役共其帷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2380:2403'>幕幄帟綬掌次師田則張幕設重帟重案司几筵凡田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2403:2426'>役則設熊席右漆几司常凡軍事建旌旗田亦如之大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2426:2449'>僕凡軍旅田役賛王鼓鼓人軍動則鼓其衆田役亦如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2449:2472'>之司弓矢殺矢鏃矢用諸田獵獸人掌罟田獸辨其名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2472:2495'>物冬獻狼夏獻麋春秋獻獸物時田則守罟及弊田令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2495:2518'>禽注于虞中凡田獸者掌其政令山虞若大田獵則萊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2518:2541'>山田之野及弊田植虞旗于中致禽而珥焉澤虞若大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2541:2567'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-7a' );" name="007-7a" class="pb">[007-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2567:2590'>田獵則萊澤野及弊田植虞旌以屬禽迹人凡田獵者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2590:2613'>受令焉禁麛卵者與其毒矢射者郊特牲季春出火為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2613:2636'>焚也然後簡其車賦而歴其卒伍而君親誓社以習軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2636:2659'>旅左之右之坐之起之以觀其習變也而流示之禽而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2659:2689'>鹽諸利以觀其不犯命也<span class='krp-note'>鹽讀為豔歆/豔於利也</span>曲禮國君春田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2689:2712'>不圍澤大夫不掩羣士不取麛卵詩吉日既張我弓既</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2712:2735'>挾我矢發彼小豝殪此大兕盧令刺荒于田也春秋傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2735:2758'>魯昭公八年蒐于紅艾蘭以為防置旃以為轅門以葛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2758:2784'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-7b' );" name="007-7b" class="pb">[007-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2784:2808'>覆質以為𣙗流旁握御轚者不得入車軌塵馬候蹄揜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2808:2831'>禽旅御者不失其馳然後射者能中過旁弗逐下從奔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2831:2836'>之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2836:2859'>　愚案艾蘭以為防以大艾草為防營也置旃以為轅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2859:2882'>　門旃旗名謂植旗以為門轅門是植車以為門舍其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2882:2906'>　五十步後表之中謂君表也覆纒質椹𣙗門闑也以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2906:2929'>　毛裘纒質之上以為門闑也流旁握握四寸謂車與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2929:2953'>　門之廣狹相值差偏以寸則轚挂於𣙗驅而不得入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2953:2979'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-8a' );" name="007-8a" class="pb">[007-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2979:3002'>　矣車軌塵塵不出轍馬候蹄發足疾遲相應也案詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='3002:3026'>　𫝊朱子謂葛作褐即裘纒質流旁握即閒容握文義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='3026:3049'>　相同攷之車之制具見於考工記輪人輿人之治御</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3049:3072'>　之名僅見於保氏五御之目是制莫難於車御莫難</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3072:3095'>　於人習莫難於戰所謂以不敎民戰是謂棄之也此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3095:3118'>　故因田車之御以閲軍旅之車習民於變為戰之備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3118:3141'>　所謂敎於田獵以習五戎是也夫羣卒伍之衆局熊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3141:3164'>　虎之氣三鼓振鐸當車徒驟趨禽獸流崩之時騎射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3164:3190'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-8b' );" name="007-8b" class="pb">[007-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3190:3213'>　驅逐之際苟御之不以其道勘失之寸則車挂馬潰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3213:3236'>　駭而莫之為射不及中而犯命之罰及之習之為易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3236:3259'>　乎噫御車節奏之法其難如此則夫御人之道又何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3259:3264'>　如哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3264:3272'>　　　苗田禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3272:3295'>大司馬中夏敎茇舍遂以苗田如蒐之法車弊獻禽以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3295:3318'>饗礿王制天子殺則下大綏諸侯殺則下小綏大夫殺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3318:3353'>則止佐車佐車止則百姓田獵<span class='krp-note'>殺獲也下偃仆之也綏/旌旗之屬佐車即周禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3353:3379'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-9a' );" name="007-9a" class="pb">[007-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3379:3389'><span class='krp-note'>逆驅之/車也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3389:3397'>　　　獮田禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3397:3420'>大司馬中秋敎治兵遂以獮田如蒐田之法羅弊致禽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3420:3443'>以祀祊肆師獮之日涖卜來嵗之戒春秋莊公八年春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3443:3471'>甲午治兵月令季秋天子乃敎於田獵以習五戎<span class='krp-note'>五戎/謂弓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3471:3485'><span class='krp-note'>矢殳矛戈㦸/之五兵也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3485:3493'>　　　狩田禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3493:3516'>大司馬中冬敎大閲遂以狩田以旌為左右和之門羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3516:3542'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-9b' );" name="007-9b" class="pb">[007-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3542:3565'>吏各帥其車徒以敘和出左右陳車徒有司平之旗居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3565:3588'>卒間以分地前後有屯百步有司巡其前後險野人為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3588:3611'>主易野車為主既陳乃設驅逆之車有司表貉于陳前</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3611:3634'>中軍以鼙令鼓鼓人皆三鼓羣司馬振鐸車徒皆作遂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3634:3657'>鼓行徒銜枚而進大獸公之小獸私之獲者取左耳及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3657:3680'>所弊鼓皆駴車徒皆譟徒乃弊致禽饁獸于郊入獻禽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3680:3703'>以享烝詩車攻田車既好駕言行狩春秋桓公四年春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3703:3711'>正月公狩于郎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3711:3738'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-10a' );" name="007-10a" class="pb">[007-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3738:3755'>　愚案郎非國内之狩故書地譏逺也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3755:3762'>　　　禷禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3762:3785'>太祝大師禷上帝詩皇矣篇是類是禡王制天子將出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3785:3792'>征類乎上帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3792:3815'>　愚案國之大事在祀與戎此為師祭也師興征伐類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3815:3828'>　于上帝言禮以敬其事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3828:3835'>　　　禡禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3835:3858'>大司馬有司表貉于陳前甸祝掌四時之田表貉之祝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3858:3885'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-10b' );" name="007-10b" class="pb">[007-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3885:3908'>號肆師凡四時之大甸獵祭表貉則為位王制禡於所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3908:3920'>征之地詩皇矣是類是禡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3920:3930'>　案禡行師之祭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3930:3937'>　　　宜禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3937:3961'>大祝大師宜于社王制天子將出征宜乎社春秋左𫝊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3961:3967'>受脹于社</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3967:3990'>　愚案宜出兵祭社之名社所以神地道主隂先王建</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3990:4013'>　國左祖右社大社左庫門之内右國社亦在公宫之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4013:4040'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-11a' );" name="007-11a" class="pb">[007-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4040:4063'>　右皆尚隂也隂主殺故誓社而田因田而習軍旅出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4063:4086'>　征祭之稱其義也然征既宜于社而又類于上帝造</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4086:4109'>　于祖禰何哉蓋生殺非王者所得私也類于上帝明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4109:4132'>　奉天討也造于祖禰示受命于廟不敢自専也曰類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4132:4155'>　曰宜曰造祭雖先後不同合周官王制泰誓言之其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4155:4164'>　義各有攸當也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4164:4171'>　　　造禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4171:4194'>大祝掌六祈以同鬼神示二曰造大師造于祖王制天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4194:4221'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-11b' );" name="007-11b" class="pb">[007-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4221:4230'>子將出征造乎禰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4230:4253'>　愚案造造而告之之祭也告于祖禰告以道其事而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4253:4276'>　致其敬也考之王制又曰受命于祖泰誓曰受命于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4276:4298'>　文考此蓋因造告卜於廟受命于祖考而後征也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4298:4307'>　　　祭馬祖禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4307:4330'>校人春祭馬祖執駒庾人掌阜馬及祭馬祖詩吉日吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4330:4339'>日維戊既伯既禱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4339:4361'>　案伯馬祖也謂天駟房星之神也禱祀而祈之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4361:4388'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-12a' );" name="007-12a" class="pb">[007-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4388:4397'>　　　祭先牧禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4397:4416'>校人夏祭先牧頒馬攻特庾人祭閑之先牧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4416:4425'>　　　祭馬社禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4425:4435'>校人秋祭馬社臧僕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4435:4444'>　　　祭馬步禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4444:4467'>校人冬祭馬步獻馬講馭夫甸祝裯牲裯馬皆掌其祝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4467:4470'>號</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4470:4479'>　　　大合軍禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4479:4506'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-12b' );" name="007-12b" class="pb">[007-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4506:4527'>大司馬及師大合軍以行禁令以救無辜伐有罪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4527:4535'>　　　誓師禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4535:4558'>士師以五戒先後刑罰一曰誓用之于軍旅大司徒施</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4558:4581'>十有二敎八曰以誓敎恤則民不怠書大禹謨禹乃㑹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4581:4607'>羣后誓于師曰濟濟有衆咸聽朕命<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>其克有勲甘誓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4607:4633'>大戰于甘乃召六卿王曰嗟六事之人予誓告汝<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>予</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4633:4658'>則孥戮汝𦙍征惟仲康肇位四海𦙍侯命掌六師羲和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4658:4682'>廢厥職酒荒于厥邑𦙍侯承王命徂征告于衆曰嗟予</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4682:4709'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-13a' );" name="007-13a" class="pb">[007-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4709:4735'>有衆<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>其爾衆士懋戒哉湯誓王曰格爾衆庶悉聽朕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4735:4761'>言<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>罔有攸赦泰誓惟十有三年春大㑹于孟津王曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4761:4787'>嗟我友邦冢君越我御事庶士明聽誓<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>時哉不可失</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4787:4810'>維戊午王次于河朔羣后以師畢㑹王乃徇師而誓曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4810:4836'>嗚呼<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>惟克永世時厥明王乃大巡六師明誓衆士王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4836:4862'>曰嗚呼我西土君子<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>維予小子無良牧誓時甲子昧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4862:4888'>爽王朝至于商郊牧野乃誓王左杖黄鉞<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>其于爾躬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4888:4892'>有戮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4892:4919'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-13b' );" name="007-13b" class="pb">[007-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4919:4927'>　　　致師禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4927:4950'>環人掌致師大司馬及致建大常比軍衆誅後至者春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4950:4973'>秋傳宣公十二年楚許伯御樂伯攝叔為右以致晉師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4973:4996'>許伯曰吾聞致師者御靡旌摩壘而還樂伯曰吾聞致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4996:5019'>師者左射以菆代御執轡御下兩馬掉鞅而還攝叔曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5019:5042'>吾聞致師者右入壘折馘執俘而還皆行其所聞而復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5042:5050'>　　　大獻禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5050:5073'>大祝軍歸獻于社則前祝大司馬若師有功則左執律</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5073:5100'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-14a' );" name="007-14a" class="pb">[007-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5100:5123'>右秉鉞以先愷樂獻于社大司樂王師大獻則令奏愷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5123:5146'>樂樂師凡軍大獻敎愷歌遂倡之眂瞭賔射皆奏其鍾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5146:5170'>鼓鼜愷獻亦如之鏄師軍大獻則鼔其愷樂春秋左傳凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5170:5193'>諸侯有四夷之功則獻于王王以警于夷中國則否諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5193:5216'>侯不相遺俘僖公二十八年五月丁未晉侯獻楚俘于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5216:5239'>王駟介百乘徒兵千文公四年甯武子曰諸侯敵王所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5239:5262'>愾而獻其功王於是乎賜之彤弓一彤矢百玈弓矢千</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5262:5285'>以覺報宴成公二年晉侯使鞏朔獻齊捷于周王弗見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5285:5312'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-14b' );" name="007-14b" class="pb">[007-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5312:5335'>使單襄公辭焉曰蠻夷戎狄不式王命淫湎毁常王命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5335:5358'>伐之則有獻捷王親受而勞之所以懲不敬勸有功也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5358:5381'>兄弟甥舅侵敗王略王命伐之告事而已不獻其功所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5381:5404'>以敬親暱禁淫慝也今叔父克遂有功於齊而奸先王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5404:5427'>之禮余雖欲於鞏伯其敢廢舊典以忝叔父夫齊甥舅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5427:5450'>之國也而大師之後也寧不淫從其欲以怒叔父抑豈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5450:5473'>不可諫誨士莊伯不能對襄公二十五年鄭伐陳入之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5473:5496'>子産獻捷于晉戎服將事晉人問陳之罪對曰昔虞閼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5496:5523'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-15a' );" name="007-15a" class="pb">[007-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5523:5546'>父為周陶正以服事我先王我先王賴其利器用也與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5546:5569'>其神明之後也庸以元女大姬配胡公而封諸陳以備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5569:5592'>三恪則我周之自出至于今是賴桓公之亂蔡人欲立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5592:5615'>其出我先君莊公奉五父而立之蔡人殺之我又與蔡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5615:5638'>人奉戴厲公至於莊宣皆我之自立夏氏之亂成公播</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5638:5661'>蕩又我之自入君所知也今陳忘周之大徳蔑我大恵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5661:5684'>弃我姻親介恃楚衆以憑陵我敝邑不可億逞我是以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5684:5707'>有徃年之告未獲成命則有我東門之役當陳隧者井</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5707:5734'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-15b' );" name="007-15b" class="pb">[007-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5734:5757'>堙木刋敝邑大懼不競而恥大姬天誘其衷啟敝邑心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5757:5780'>陳知其罪授手于我用敢獻功晉人曰何故戎服對曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5780:5803'>我先君武莊為平桓卿士城濮之役文公布命曰各服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5803:5826'>舊職命我文公戎服輔王以授楚捷不敢廢王命故也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5826:5849'>士莊伯不能詰乃受之成公二年鄭皇戍如楚獻捷昭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5849:5872'>公十年季平子伐莒取郠獻俘十七年晉荀吳滅陸渾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5872:5879'>獻俘于文宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5879:5889'>　　　釋奠獻馘禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5889:5916'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-16a' );" name="007-16a" class="pb">[007-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5916:5939'>大祝及軍歸反行舍奠王制出征執有罪反釋奠于學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5939:5945'>以訊馘告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5945:5968'>　愚案訊者問其首惡馘者截其左耳夫執訊獲醜而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5968:5991'>　反舍奠于先聖先師以是告之者蓋始出征受成于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5991:6014'>　學今師還以武功告成于文徳之地明不専恃乎威</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='6014:6037'>　戮而必任之以徳禮也昔僖公在頖獻馘而國人以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='6037:6049'>　文武頌之者亦以此歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='6049:6057'>　　　大均禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='6057:6084'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-16b' );" name="007-16b" class="pb">[007-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='6084:6107'>大宗伯大均之禮恤衆也大司馬均守平則以安邦國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='6107:6130'>大司徒以土均之法辨五物九等制天下之地征以作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='6130:6153'>民職以令地貢以斂財賦以均齊天下之政小司徒受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='6153:6176'>邦國之比要乃㑹萬民之卒伍而用之五人為伍五伍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='6176:6199'>為兩四兩為卒五卒為旅五旅為師五師為軍以起軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='6199:6222'>旅以作田役以比追胥以令貢賦乃分地域而辨其守</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='6222:6245'>施其職而平其政土均掌平土地之政以均地守以均</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='6245:6268'>地事以均地貢均人掌均人民牛馬車輦之力政以嵗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='6268:6295'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-17a' );" name="007-17a" class="pb">[007-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='6295:6309'>上下書康誥昔君文武丕平富</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='6309:6317'>　　　大役禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='6317:6340'>大宗伯大役之禮任衆也小司徒大軍旅帥其衆庶小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='6340:6363'>軍旅巡役乃均土地以稽其人民而周知其數上地家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6363:6386'>七人可任也者家三人中地家六人可任也者家五人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6386:6409'>下地家五人可任也者家二人凡起徒役毋過家一人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6409:6432'>以其餘為羨唯田與追胥竭作鄉大夫以嵗時登其夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6432:6455'>家之衆寡辨其可任者國中自七尺以及六十野自六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6455:6482'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-17b' );" name="007-17b" class="pb">[007-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6482:6505'>尺以及六十有五皆征之其舍者國中貴者賢者能者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6505:6528'>服公事者老者疾者皆舍大司馬凡令賦以地與民制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6528:6551'>之上地食者參之二其民可用者家三人中地食者半</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6551:6574'>其民可用者二家五人下地食者參之一其民可用者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6574:6597'>家二人大役與慮事屬其植受其要以待考而賞誅縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6597:6620'>士邦有大役聚衆庶則各掌其縣春秋左傳凡土功龍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6620:6643'>見而畢務戒事也火見而致用水昬正而栽日至而畢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6643:6651'>　　　大封禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6651:6678'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-18a' );" name="007-18a" class="pb">[007-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6678:6701'>大宗伯大封之禮合衆也大司徒辨其邦國都鄙之數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6701:6724'>制其畿疆而溝封之大司馬制畿封國以正邦國形方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6724:6747'>氏掌制邦國之地役而正其封疆無有華離之地司几</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6747:6770'>筵凡封國王位設黼依内史凡命諸侯及孤卿大夫則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6770:6793'>冊命之大宗伯王命諸侯則儐大司徒凡建邦國以土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='6793:6816'>圭土其地而制其役諸公之地封疆方五百里其食者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='6816:6839'>半諸侯之地封疆方四百里其食者參之一諸伯之地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='6839:6862'>封疆方百三里其食者參之一諸子之地封疆方二百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='6862:6889'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-18b' );" name="007-18b" class="pb">[007-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='6889:6912'>里其食者四之一諸男之地封疆方百里其食者四之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='6912:6935'>一凡造都鄙制為地域而封溝之以其室數制之不易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='6935:6958'>之地家百畝一易之地家二百畝再易之地家三百畝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='6958:6981'>　愚案大司徒論公侯伯子男之地各以封疆言而其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='6981:7004'>　食者或半或參之一或四之一參諸王制以田言孟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='7004:7027'>　子以班禄言蓋皆専主田禄此正周禮所謂食者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='7027:7050'>　大抵周禮所載凡五等通以封疆言兼附庸在其内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='7050:7073'>　王制孟子凡三等専以田禄言附庸不在其列此所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='7073:7100'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-19a' );" name="007-19a" class="pb">[007-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='7100:7123'>　以有多寡之殊也嘗考周公之封於魯太公之封於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='7123:7146'>　齊孟子所謂侯方百里也然魯頌有曰王曰叔父建</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='7146:7169'>　爾元子乃命魯公俾侯于東錫之山川土田附庸又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='7169:7192'>　曰奄有龜蒙遂荒大東至于海邦淮夷來同此豈魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='7192:7215'>　方百里所能容乎左傳有曰昔召康公命我先君太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='7215:7238'>　公夾輔周室賜我先君履東至于海西至于河南至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='7238:7261'>　于穆陵北至于無棣此豈齊方百里所能容乎要之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='7261:7284'>　周之封爵惟杞宋為上公齊魯爵皆侯侯之封疆方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='7284:7311'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-19b' );" name="007-19b" class="pb">[007-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='7311:7334'>　四百里其食者參之一食者參之一則封疆百里有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='7334:7357'>　竒正孟子王制所謂侯方百里魯頌所謂錫之土田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='7357:7380'>　者也其餘封疆迨三百里正魯頌所謂錫之附庸如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='7380:7403'>　魯有邾葛顓臾之類是已職方氏凡邦國千里封公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='7403:7426'>　以方五百里則四公方四百里則六侯方三百里則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='7426:7449'>　七伯方二百里則二十五子方百里則百男以周知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='7449:7467'>　天下周易師上六大君有命開國承家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='7467:7478'>　　　大封告后土禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='7478:7505'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '007-20a' );" name="007-20a" class="pb">[007-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='7505:7528'>大宗伯王大封則先告后土大祝建邦國先告后土用</span><br/>
